    <p>
      WebP has wider support than AVIF — roughly 97% of global browsers support WebP versus 92% for AVIF. Both are supported in Chrome, Firefox, Safari, and Edge. The gap mainly comes from older browsers and some niche mobile browsers. For most audiences, the 5% difference is negligible. You can serve AVIF with a WebP fallback using the <code>&lt;picture&gt;</code> element, which covers both sets of browsers.
